Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.59,0:00:06.60,Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.62,0:00:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- I bought this.\N- Oh! You changed your cellphone?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Then with this teacher,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:14.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- you can watch that drama!\N- But I don't know how to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.82,0:00:17.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- Please help me.\N- You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.82,0:00:21.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- Is that the reason why you called me?\N- Yes, help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:24.11,Main,,0,0,0,,You know in class earlier, I know\Nyou're in YouTube or Twitter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.13,0:00:26.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm not on Twitter.\N- Then you're on Instagram?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:29.70,Main,,0,0,0,,- Well... on an insta-live.\N- That's it, live streaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.72,0:00:33.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you,\Ndon't stream during class!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.66,0:00:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,You should do that when you get home!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- Okay, I'm going home.\N- No, that's not what I meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.24,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Look, look...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.26,0:00:43.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Wait Mother Teresa,\Nbring me to life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:48.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- Come on! Come on!\N- Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:52.03,Main,,0,0,0,,Whoa, great!\NWhere did you press it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.49,0:01:01.91,New,,0,0,0,,SUPRISE ENDING AFTER FIVE MINUTES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:06.63,Main,,0,0,0,,#SURPRISEGIFT
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.36,0:01:16.50,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! You're slacking off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:18.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.33,0:01:24.33,Main,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:28.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho, let's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.42,0:01:31.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- What?\N- Since the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.80,Main,,0,0,0,,They asked me if I'd be interested\Nin a full-time position in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.82,0:01:38.66,Main,,0,0,0,,I thought I should take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.39,0:01:43.21,Main,,0,0,0,,From now on,\NI'm going to get a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.23,0:01:45.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- What about your band?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:52.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- What about your band?\N- That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:55.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Well... we didn't get any audition at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.19,0:01:58.07,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not very excited about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,I think it's time to face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.85,0:02:06.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And when I think about Chiho,\NI can't work part-time all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.82,0:02:08.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't continue like that forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.85,0:02:11.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- That's why...\N- That's not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:15.37,Main,,0,0,0,,what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:17.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can become\Na world-famous musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- I really believe it.\N- What..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- I will chase a dream like that?\N- Are you going to run away?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:29.44,Main,,0,0,0,,What I want is...\NI want Chiho to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.46,0:02:31.27,Main,,0,0,0,,That's what I really want!\NSo I got a job properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:35.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Then why are you giving up?\NAre you wearing a suit while on the train
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.87,Main,,0,0,0,,so your dreams will come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.89,0:02:42.37,Main,,0,0,0,,I can wait forever for your dreams though!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:46.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,This thing kind of thing...\Nis not what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:57.67,Main,,0,0,0,,There are things more\Nimportant than dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:03:01.09,Main,,0,0,0,,Why don't you understand my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.36,0:03:09.54,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...\NShe doesn't want to marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.56,0:03:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm not worthy of her anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:15.70,Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe she's moving out of the house now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.72,0:03:18.90,Main,,0,0,0,,What are you mumbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.92,0:03:23.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- Senpai, please let me leave early!\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.16,0:03:27.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm really sorry!\N- Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:29.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:33.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.09,0:03:47.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho! Chiho, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.82,0:03:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- Chiho!\N- Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.89,0:04:02.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.13,0:04:04.44,Main,,0,0,0,,How's your part-time job? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.46,0:04:06.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:08.82,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.00,0:04:19.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.00,0:04:25.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me... it is for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:30.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah, If you're going to work\Nfor a company, you will need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.35,0:04:38.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I got out of control because of\Nthe suddenness of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.33,0:04:41.80,Main,,0,0,0,,But I thought you were\Nserious about our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.82,0:04:46.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.13,0:04:51.17,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, I was going to surprise you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.01,Main,,0,0,0,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,On how you behaved yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.49,0:05:06.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I know you were so serious about my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:12.80,Main,,0,0,0,,And yet... I doubted your love.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I'm such a stupid man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Junpei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:23.47,Main,,0,0,0,,You are the best woman in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:27.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I will cherish you for the rest of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.49,0:05:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,That woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,No way! You've got a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:02.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- I still want to have fun.\N- Are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:08.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Well, if I didn't found anyone else,\NI'd be happy to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.16,0:06:12.47,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?\NBut you can still play with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:14.49,Main,,0,0,0,,Chiho! Chiho, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:20.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- Chiho!\N- Don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.33,0:06:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Why are you saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.33,0:06:24.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:26.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Let me be alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:39.31,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Wow... so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:53.54,Main,,0,0,0,,How can I get back my suit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:05.47,Main,,0,0,0,,This man on the balcony,\Ndid he got home safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:08.98,Main,,0,0,0,,He wears only briefs,\Neven if you get off the balcony safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:10.98,Main,,0,0,0,,How the hell are he supposed to move?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But you teacher is like Junpei too.\NBe careful not to be fooled.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.28,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't compare others on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:17.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, I want to see\Na picture of your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.85,0:07:20.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- Why?\N- Let me see if she's like Chiho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.82,0:07:22.80,Main,,0,0,0,,She's not like Chiho!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.82,0:07:24.80,Main,,0,0,0,,A woman knows a lot more than men.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- No, no need for it.\N- It's in there, isn't it? Let me see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.00,0:07:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it! Risa, stop!\NStop it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:49.57,Main,,0,0,0,,CLOSED ROOM GAME
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:58.66,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.66,0:08:11.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Hey! Somebody! Is anyone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.00,0:08:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.23,0:08:18.60,Main,,0,0,0,,You just got have a good rest until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.00,0:08:25.14,Main,,0,0,0,,Is this a prank or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,As expected from a leading popular actor,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.33,0:08:33.31,Main,,0,0,0,,that's the kind of idea they think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,But you are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:38.80,Main,,0,0,0,,Then what's your point?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.82,0:08:42.37,Main,,0,0,0,,You've got me trapped in a\Nplace like this, is it for money?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.39,0:08:45.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I do not want money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.54,Main,,0,0,0,,I just want to play a game with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:50.64,Main,,0,0,0,,Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.66,0:08:54.87,Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. You're betting your life on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:09:00.64,Main,,0,0,0,,The rules are simple, all you\Nhave to do is answer my questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,But don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:09.17,Main,,0,0,0,,If you don't answer\Nhonestly, you will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this nonsense...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:13.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What is this joke now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.82,0:09:17.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, the first question:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Have you ever done a thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.92,0:09:23.98,Main,,0,0,0,,just for your personal desires?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:26.11,Main,,0,0,0,,There isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.13,0:09:28.33,Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.69,0:09:36.98,Main,,0,0,0,,No matter how long it takes,\Nthe night will always end!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.00,0:09:39.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.66,0:09:46.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I've never brought anyone down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,The only reason I'm in this\Nposition is because of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.82,0:09:53.59,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:08.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I told you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,If you give a false\Nanswer, I'm going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.66,0:10:22.47,Main,,0,0,0,,About 20 years ago,\NI went to a fellow actor's place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:28.47,Main,,0,0,0,,I got an offer to play the leading\Nrole in a stage play and I want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.49,0:10:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,But he took it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:37.93,Main,,0,0,0,,So I did a little work on the set.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:42.17,Main,,0,0,0,,That guy just happened\Nto be in an accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.19,0:10:44.17,Main,,0,0,0,,and I got the lead role.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:48.50,Main,,0,0,0,,The night will definitely come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:54.70,Main,,0,0,0,,If you call that entrapment.\NI think you've caved in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.72,0:10:57.07,Main,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.09,0:11:01.98,Main,,0,0,0,,You, are you that guy from back then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.31,Main,,0,0,0,,You're trying to get revenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:08.93,Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, next question, 12 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:12.54,Main,,0,0,0,,your manager caused the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Please answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.73,Main,,0,0,0,,How many times do I\Nhave to say the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:19.75,Main,,0,0,0,,Enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:27.42,Main,,0,0,0,,You want me to say\Nthat the accident was my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:33.47,Main,,0,0,0,,He was a psychiatrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.49,0:11:36.47,Main,,0,0,0,,He told me it was my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:40.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I yelled at him and stuff like that,\Nso he has no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:46.07,Main,,0,0,0,,But you know what? I'm\Nunder a lot more stress than him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.09,0:11:49.14,Main,,0,0,0,,In an industry where merit\Nis the only thing that counts,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.16,0:11:52.21,Main,,0,0,0,,I have to keep being a popular actor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.23,0:11:55.69,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's the manager's job!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:00.47,Main,,0,0,0,,After all, he's a sick man at heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:06.40,Main,,0,0,0,,He drinks tranquilizers in\Nlarge doses even before driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.75,Main,,0,0,0,,And that's how he got into an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.75,0:12:13.73,Main,,0,0,0,,You're satisfied with this much talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.75,0:12:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,That's good. Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:20.24,Main,,0,0,0,,That's enough!\NWho the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:26.06,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you love your wife and daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.06,0:12:30.80,Main,,0,0,0,,What the hell, suddenly you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:33.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! You're good at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:39.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- Here you go...\N- Wow! Delicious looking fruits are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- Thank you.\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.66,0:12:43.98,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:47.83,Main,,0,0,0,,Of course, in a marriage,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:52.11,Main,,0,0,0,,I love my wife and my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.13,0:12:57.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Now then, how many\Nchildren do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:08.00,Main,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.19,0:13:19.57,Main,,0,0,0,,Are you... Yosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:26.80,Main,,0,0,0,,More than 20 years ago, before I was\Nmarried and before my daughter was born,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:31.83,Main,,0,0,0,,I loved a woman once other than my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:38.46,Main,,0,0,0,,He was born to her.\NThat's Yosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.93,Main,,0,0,0,,But if an illegitimate child is discovered,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:47.95,Main,,0,0,0,,my acting career will be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:53.04,Main,,0,0,0,,In exchange of continuing\Nto pay child support,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:57.39,Main,,0,0,0,,I asked them to keep the truth quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.59,0:14:05.01,Main,,0,0,0,,If Yosuke heard about that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:07.24,Main,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter if he\Nhave a grudge against me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:12.44,Main,,0,0,0,,But Yosuke,\NI want you to understand one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:17.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't abandon you and your mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.29,0:14:20.14,Main,,0,0,0,,I loved your mother.\NI'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.16,0:14:25.01,Main,,0,0,0,,I don't care about any of that!\NQuickly tell me the answer to my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:29.36,Main,,0,0,0,,How many children do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:37.60,Main,,0,0,0,,I have two children.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:40.47,Main,,0,0,0,,That's incorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:43.17,Main,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?\NI have no one but only him and my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:45.44,Main,,0,0,0,,That's all. I didn't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.98,Main,,0,0,0,,The correct answer is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:53.66,Main,,0,0,0,,"I have only one child."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:15:01.14,Main,,0,0,0,,So Yosuke is not my child?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.16,0:15:05.70,Main,,0,0,0,,To cheat me out of my money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:11.40,Main,,0,0,0,,No. He is indeed your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:14.27,Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.29,0:15:16.37,Main,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.39,0:15:21.29,Main,,0,0,0,,The one who is not your\Nchild is your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.26,0:15:29.54,Main,,0,0,0,,What nonsense...\NThat can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.56,0:15:32.70,Main,,0,0,0,,You can understand, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:36.47,Main,,0,0,0,,"I once had feelings for a\Nwoman who was not my wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.04,Main,,0,0,0,,Only if it's you only.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:43.00,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:52.57,Main,,0,0,0,,You can understand, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.59,0:15:56.60,Main,,0,0,0,,"I once had feelings for a\Nwoman who was not my wife."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.62,0:16:00.31,Main,,0,0,0,,Only if it's you only.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.33,0:16:01.80,Main,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'll draw you a bear too.\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:09.19,Main,,0,0,0,,I'll draw a lot here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:17.03,Main,,0,0,0,,You are the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.73,Main,,0,0,0,,What does this mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.87,Main,,0,0,0,,It's just like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.89,0:16:33.27,Main,,0,0,0,,I too loved a man who was not my husband\Nand gave birth to my daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:40.54,Main,,0,0,0,,You understand, don't you?\NHey, honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.56,0:16:58.40,Main,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.79,0:17:12.90,Main,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, you're being very presentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.92,0:17:14.64,Main,,0,0,0,,She've prepared so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:18.14,Main,,0,0,0,,That amazing room,\Ndid she build it all by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:22.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- I don't think so.\N- It's a fad - DIY.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:26.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'm going home.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.26,0:17:28.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- Goodbye.\N- No, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.60,Main,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like the scary wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- Let's watch one more...\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.89,0:17:34.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I just bought it but\Nit's already broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:36.67,Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so black!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:39.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- Where's your charger?\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't bring one.\NIf you have a spare, lend it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:44.64,Main,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:49.34,Main,,0,0,0,,What is these?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:52.54,Main,,0,0,0,,That's a lot of choices!\NWow, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.56,0:17:56.11,Main,,0,0,0,,Unseasonal Santa Claus,\Nthanks for the surprise gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.83,Main,,0,0,0,,This will bring me back to life too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- Well, I'm going home.\N- Wait for this.
